/text<CR>  search            | x/X          del char (left)|------------------
/<CR>      search next       | dmotion      delete block   | FILES
n/N        search next/prev. | dd           delete line    | :w   save file
?text<CR>  search backward   | D            delete to EOL  | :W   write block
?<CR>      search prev. back.| ymotion      copy block     | :r   insert file
'm       go to marked line   | yy           copy line      | :q   quit
`m       go to marker        | p/P          paste (before) | :q!  abandon
mm       set marker          | f/t<char>    go (on)to char |
